a-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EdtKBq1cV2w</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/36e_fKooyJ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F36e_fKooyJ0&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=3f3fff24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/36e_fKooyJ0</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">立場記者受襲倒地</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ifldMBQJRmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FifldMBQJRmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=7476b1b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ifldMBQJRmo</a><br />\n（片段太多，未能一一列出）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">805</span></strong></span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">荃灣</span></span></strong>（受傷：黑衫、街坊； 打手：撐警福建幫）<br />\n-有片、有記者「壹傳媒」「香港01」..<br />\n-沒有打手被捕<br />\n-多名市民受傷<br />\n-最重傷者手腳被斬至見骨，頭部亦有傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GwJrSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GwJrSU.jpg&h=7aa5f556&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTDzyxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTDzyxV.jpg&h=a2eeeedd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sc8DfMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsc8DfMg.jpg&h=2d378784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>相關報導</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20190818/20750438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F20750438&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=2d622e86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F20750438&h=45667afc\" data-auto-link target=